\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42102995&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">钦念以忱 发表于 2018-12-28 19:39</font></a><br />\r\n这么说的话，第一季里退部的斋藤葵就是在野党头号干将，带头冲锋，唯一投反对票的，还能察觉出吹武帝是潜 ...</div><br />\n而且看第一季，最先传出本来是明日香做部长，明日香不想做才给了晴香这种言论的是低音部。<br />\r\n这套路怎么和朱棣的“太祖本来想让我做太子”一样呢。<br />\r\n在野党一套随风倒，反倒是小号、低音部这两个部长派系在选拔中吃亏，部长自己的萨克斯却除了葵外全部入选，不能不让部员怀疑晴香是既想攘外又想安内啊。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"406","username":"老仓唯","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"406","dbdateline":"1546000228","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42103602","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"s0534146","authorid":"264318","dateline":"2018-12-28 20:44","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42100404&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">老仓唯 发表于 2018-12-28 15:43</font></a><br />\n我在B站重看京吹第一季<br />\r\n每次秀一鸡出场就有弹幕说部费<br />\r\n秀一鸡太惨了，明明就这一个黑点，弹幕里却像是被 ...</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/036.png\" />你知道秀一是为什么交不起部费吗<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/047.png\" />是氪金氪得没钱了啊～～没钱了啊～～钱了啊～～了啊～～啊～～<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 HUAWEI CLT-AL00, Android 8.1.0上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.0.4-play","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"407","username":"s0534146","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"407","dbdateline":"1546001088","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"42103689","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"青菜子","authorid":"238889","dateline":"2018-12-28 20:53","message":"<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/carton2017/018.gif\" />伞哥好歹还是非钦定的头号种子,空降吹奏部三把手会计职务,比小组长高到不知道哪里去了,实力还是超强的.深不可测","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"408","username":"青菜子","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"408","dbd